reviewText: It's a little bit too predictable without any significant memorable moments. Not worthy of five stars!!
This is easily one of the best movies it was so good.

Summer is not a happy camper. Until she finds an orphaned dog that her friend dubs as Shadow.  What happens next is a perfect example of judging from what you see on the outside and not knowing what's on the inside.
A great family film with hero's and villains, not especially the usual ones.
My youngest daughter loves this movie. She watched it several times.
Saw this on Villa, and added it to my collection, thanks for having it available.
Touching kids movie - Our granddaughters loved it
It was a lovely story for families.
